 * <p>crazy idea for y’all to consider: after a proposal has gone through all the stages and gets merged into the spec, change the <code>body</code> start tag in the HTML source of the proposal to this:</p>
<pre><code class="language-html">&lt;body onload='(function() { location.href = &quot;https://tc39.es/ecma262/multipage/&quot; + location.hash; })()'&gt;
</code></pre>
